				<td colspan="2"><span>I have been reading quite a few posts lately that talk about how they use invis ring or selo's song of travel to break charm.  In the old days it used to be really easy to just dot your pet and charm would break and then you could just chant your target down.  I really liked that method of breaking charm, and found that the same method can still be used if you just dispell your pet.  Dispell breaks charm ... chant down.</span></td>
